PN,36401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FA newly qualified driver who partied
OL,7,Fand went on a skiing holiday in the
OL,8,Fmonths after killing two friends in a
OL,9,Fcrash has been locked up.
OL,11,FMadeleine Lonsdale, 18, passed her
OL,12,Ftest 12 weeks before she crashed her
OL,13,Fcar into a tree in the village of
OL,14,FMarston, Lincolnshire, on 20 June last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FHer passengers Harrison Carter, 18,
OL,18,Fand George Stephenson, 17, who had
OL,19,Frecently finished their A-level exams,
OL,20,Fdied at the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
