OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FLonsdale, who pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fcausing the teenagers' deaths by
OL,8,Fcareless driving, was sentenced to 14
OL,9,Fmonths in youth detention.
OL,11,FProsecutor Steven Taylor told Lincoln
OL,12,FCrown Court the boys were passengers
OL,13,Fin Lonsdale's Kia Niro when they went
OL,14,Fto a petrol station off the A1 in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of the morning.
OL,17,FThe court heard she raced another car
OL,18,Fat 100mph during the trip to buy
OL,19,Fsnacks, alcohol and vapes.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FMr Taylor said: "She took a left turn
OL,7,Fdown a rural country road and ... down
OL,8,Fthat road for a distance, evidently
OL,9,Faccelerated to over 70mph.
OL,11,F"In due course she failed to negotiate
OL,12,Fa right-hand bend further along the
OL,13,Froad."
OL,15,FHe added: "It appears she misjudged
OL,16,Fthe distance to the first bend and
OL,17,Ffailed to slow down at all on her
OL,18,Fapproach."
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUuD@FO]wD@KOUzD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FThe court heard that the car was
OL,7,Ftravelling at 76mph seconds before it
OL,8,Fcollided with the tree in Toll Bar
OL,9,FRoad and then landed on its side.
OL,11,FThe unlit road had a 60mph limit, Mr
OL,12,FTaylor said, and a sign warning of the
OL,13,Fupcoming bend.
OL,15,FAnother car driven by a teenage friend
OL,16,Fwas following Lonsdale's vehicle but
OL,17,Fmanaged to avoid the collision, the
OL,18,Fprosecutor told the court.
OL,20,F'Insult to injury'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FMr Taylor said Lonsdale and the other
OL,7,Fdriver decided to "see how fast their
OL,8,Frespective vehicles could go" and
OL,9,F"effectively raced each other" before
OL,10,Fthe crash.
OL,12,FLonsdale, who suffered a minor wrist
OL,13,Finjury, continued to post on social
OL,14,Fmedia in the months after the
OL,15,Fincident, the court heard.
OL,26,@oD@SOUpD@]O]qD@AOUqD@^O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FIn a statement, Harrison's mother
OL,7,FSarah Carter said it "adds insult to
OL,8,Finjury" that Lonsdale was "partying
OL,9,Frepeatedly" and "choreographing
OL,10,FTikToks" while she planned her son's
OL,11,Ffuneral.
OL,13,FShe added: "Harry was taken from us
OL,14,Fbecause Madeleine chose to speed.
OL,16,F"He will never be able to celebrate
OL,17,Fthe amazing exam results that he
OL,18,Fachieved."
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@GO]pD@[OUqD@KO]qD@QOUrD@HO]uD@
OL,26,ALOUxD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FGeorge's mother Victoria Stephenson
OL,7,Ftold the court: "We will never see him
OL,8,Fgraduate or find a job after
OL,9,Funiversity.
OL,11,F"We didn't get to celebrate his 18th
OL,12,Fbirthday with him, instead we had his
OL,13,Ffuneral."
OL,15,FShe said that when Lonsdale went on a
OL,16,Fskiing trip, delaying her first court
OL,17,Fappearance by two weeks, it "only
OL,18,Fadded to the torment".
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@AOUuD@IO]yD@]OUzD@UO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FMitigating for Lonsdale, of Squires
OL,7,FView, Long Bennington, Lincolnshire,
OL,8,FJohn McNally said: "She knows that
OL,9,Fthere is nothing she can say, do, to
OL,10,Ftake the pain away.
OL,12,F"She knows it will weigh heavily on
OL,13,Fher for the rest of her life.
OL,15,F"Her regret for what happened is deep
OL,16,Fand ... her friends will remain, and
OL,17,Fare, in her thoughts."
OL,19,FLonsdale, who appeared upset in the
OL,20,Fdock, was disqualified from driving
OL,21,Ffor three years.
OL,26,@pD@TOUtD@AOUwD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
