OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Det Sgt
OL,7,FAdam Doona, of Lincolnshire Police,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This collision was down to the
OL,9,Fspeed and inexperience of Madeleine
OL,10,FLonsdale.
OL,12,F"Tragically, as a result of her
OL,13,Fdriving, friends who should have been
OL,14,Fcelebrating starting the next stage of
OL,15,Ftheir lives are no longer with us.
OL,17,F"When someone obtains their full
OL,18,Fdriving licence, they need to remember
OL,19,Fthat this is purely the start of their
OL,20,Fdriving career.
OL,26,@pD@GOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773576180
OL,3,C18-year-old woman who caused friends'
OL,4,Cdeaths in crash sentenced
OL,6,F"A lack of experience and failing to
OL,7,Fdrive according to the rules of the
OL,8,Froad in this case, will leave an
OL,9,Findelible mark on all those involved
OL,10,Ffor the rest of their lives."
